Locus:
  Case: 3
Title: Master Ma Was Restless
---
Great Master Ma was restless. The chief of the courtyard
asked, "Venerable, so what have your esteemed hopes of recent days
been?"

Great Master said, "Sun Face Buddha, Moon Face Buddha."
